1
00:00:49,159 --> 00:00:50,759
What do you mean, suspected HIV infection?

2
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:52,399
What the hell is "suspected HIV infection"?

3
00:00:53,399 --> 00:00:54,719
I just came in for a teeth cleaning.

4
00:00:54,960 --> 00:00:56,159
What disease are you cursing me with?

5
00:00:56,880 --> 00:00:57,799
Are you out of your mind?

6
00:00:58,000 --> 00:00:59,600
Your test result is a bit abnormal.

7
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:01,520
We're obligated to inform you of this.

8
00:01:01,679 --> 00:01:03,280
And we hope you'll agree to a retest.

9
00:01:03,479 --> 00:01:04,359
Retest for what?

10
00:01:04,760 --> 00:01:06,200
I just have an oral ulcer from stress.

11
00:01:07,040 --> 00:01:07,840
You just wait right there!

12
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:10,599
Come on, come, come, come.

13
00:01:10,879 --> 00:01:11,640
Everyone, come over here. Sir!

14
00:01:11,799 --> 00:01:12,920
Come on, all of you, get over here.

15
00:01:13,280 --> 00:01:13,840
Come on, come on.

16
00:01:14,799 --> 00:01:16,319
All of you, take a good look.

17
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:17,359
I...

18
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:19,719
don't smoke, drink, gamble, or do drugs.

19
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:21,040
I'm a true man of virtue.

20
00:01:21,599 --> 00:01:22,760
Tell me, say it!

21
00:01:22,879 --> 00:01:23,599
You're saying I've got what?

22
00:01:23,920 --> 00:01:24,519
That disease?

23
00:01:24,719 --> 00:01:25,120
What?!

24
00:01:25,319 --> 00:01:27,400
Ridiculous! Beyond ridiculous!

25
00:01:28,040 --> 00:01:28,599
Where's the director?

26
00:01:28,799 --> 00:01:29,640
Get your director out here!

27
00:01:29,840 --> 00:01:31,120
I want an explanation today!

28
00:01:31,599 --> 00:01:33,079
Sir, please calm down for a moment.

29
00:01:33,359 --> 00:01:34,719
We completely understand how you feel.

30
00:01:34,879 --> 00:01:36,239
Please don't disturb the other patients, okay?

31
00:01:36,480 --> 00:01:37,280
Cut the crap.

32
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:38,760
Could you stay calm? Hands off!

33
00:01:38,959 --> 00:01:40,920
You bunch of quacks, not one decent person here.

34
00:01:41,519 --> 00:01:42,560
Take the instruments to be sterilized first.

35
00:01:42,599 --> 00:01:43,480
I'll handle the rest.

36
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:45,239
Sir, please calm down first.

37
00:01:45,319 --> 00:01:46,840
Can we talk this through properly?

38
00:01:47,079 --> 00:01:48,120
How am I supposed to stay calm?

39
00:01:49,879 --> 00:01:50,480
Where are you going?

40
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:51,480
Where do you think you're going?

41
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:52,359
Where are you off to?

42
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:53,439
Let me tell you.

43
00:01:53,719 --> 00:01:54,840
Until I get an explanation today,

44
00:01:54,959 --> 00:01:56,159
nobody is leaving through that door.

45
00:01:56,439 --> 00:01:58,280
You're really something, you know that?

46
00:01:58,640 --> 00:02:00,560
Why demand an explanation from the doctors?

47
00:02:00,719 --> 00:02:01,200
Yeah.

48
00:02:01,319 --> 00:02:02,879
Besides, it's just a suspected case.

49
00:02:03,079 --> 00:02:03,920
Even if you really were diagnosed,

50
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,359
you should reflect on yourself.

51
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:07,280
Maybe your private life isn't so clean.

52
00:02:07,519 --> 00:02:09,039
Say that again. I dare you, say it again!

53
00:02:10,439 --> 00:02:11,919
It must be your own problem.

54
00:02:11,919 --> 00:02:12,280
You...

55
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:13,719
And you're blaming the doctor?

56
00:02:13,759 --> 00:02:15,000
All of you, hold on.

57
00:02:15,039 --> 00:02:16,479
Don't leave! Nobody leaves!

58
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:19,919
Nobody is leaving!

59
00:02:20,039 --> 00:02:21,400
What are you doing? Let go!

60
00:02:22,159 --> 00:02:23,000
Let go!

61
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:24,439
You!

62
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:25,360
I'll beat you to death!

63
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:30,680
He's actually throwing punches!

64
00:02:30,759 --> 00:02:31,560
Why are you hitting a doctor?

65
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:34,599
Call the police, quick! Call the police!

66
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:42,520
What if I get infected? Tell me that!

67
00:03:02,159 --> 00:03:02,800
Director Zeng

68
00:03:03,159 --> 00:03:04,319
We had an occupational exposure here.

69
00:03:04,719 --> 00:03:05,479
Occupational exposure?

70
00:03:05,599 --> 00:03:06,039
Yes.

71
00:03:06,159 --> 00:03:07,840
That patient's test results just came back.

72
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:09,319
Dr. Jiang, he...

73
00:03:09,439 --> 00:03:10,120
Did he take PEP?

74
00:03:10,599 --> 00:03:11,199
Let's go.

75
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:11,919
Come on.

76
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:22,599
This had nothing to do with you.

77
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:24,479
Why did you take that hit for me?

78
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:28,960
I was passing by.

79
00:03:30,199 --> 00:03:30,759
Just a reflex.

80
00:03:30,919 --> 00:03:31,759
You really are something.

81
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:33,599
Dr. Tang only meant well.

82
00:03:33,879 --> 00:03:34,919
How can you talk like that?

83
00:03:35,159 --> 00:03:35,639
Tang Yi.

84
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:37,080
You okay? Are you hurt?

85
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:42,080
Barging in without knocking,

86
00:03:42,479 --> 00:03:43,560
not even wearing protection.

87
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:45,439
You want even more people exposed?

88
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:55,840
Dr. Jiang has had a really rough day.

89
00:03:56,879 --> 00:03:57,560
How about this,

90
00:03:57,919 --> 00:03:58,840
dinner's on me tonight.

91
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,240
Calm your nerves.

92
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,159
I'll eat. Are you sure you're paying?

93
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:03,680
I...

94
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:05,520
Still cracking jokes?

95
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:08,400
Guess you're not as bad off as I thought.

96
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:09,400
Mentor.

97
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:12,400
Don't worry.

98
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:14,840
Lucky you took PEP right away.

99
00:04:15,439 --> 00:04:17,199
That's the crucial part.

100
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:19,720
And the success rate of PEP now

101
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,519
is already over 95%.

102
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,319
Don't worry about work.

103
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:26,319
We'll get someone to cover your shifts.

104
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:28,600
Your salary and bonuses stay the same.

105
00:04:28,839 --> 00:04:29,879
The most important thing now

106
00:04:30,319 --> 00:04:32,959
is to go home and rest properly.

107
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:34,680
During this time, if you have any

108
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:36,040
fever, weakness,

109
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:37,120
or fatigue symptoms,

110
00:04:37,639 --> 00:04:38,680
call me right away.

111
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:39,759
Don't try to tough it out.

112
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:42,720
We're all waiting for you to come back.

113
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:01,519
Recently, several consumers exposed

114
00:05:01,639 --> 00:05:03,800
the chaos of unlicensed clinics in Linhai

115
00:05:04,079 --> 00:05:06,319
Victim Ms. Chen and her husband Mr. Yang

116
00:05:06,519 --> 00:05:08,279
agreed to our phone interview.

117
00:05:20,399 --> 00:05:21,160
What are you doing here?

118
00:05:22,839 --> 00:05:24,319
Repaying a favor to Dr. Jiang.

119
00:05:24,759 --> 00:05:26,759
After all, you got hurt because of me.

120
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:27,639
I'm

121
00:05:27,959 --> 00:05:28,839
here to cook you a meal.

122
00:05:29,240 --> 00:05:30,040
That's not too much, right?

123
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,199
No need.

124
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,279
Just go home.

125
00:05:38,319 --> 00:05:40,560
Don't you know how HIV is transmitted?

126
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,319
I'm not afraid, why are you?

127
00:05:43,839 --> 00:05:44,959
You're overthinking it.

128
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:46,759
My place

129
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:48,439
doesn't have any spare slippers.

130
00:05:49,279 --> 00:05:50,160
I can't host you.

131
00:05:51,279 --> 00:05:52,720
Knew you'd say that.

132
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:56,079
So I

133
00:05:57,160 --> 00:05:58,120
brought my own.

134
00:06:18,839 --> 00:06:21,519
Your home really matches your personality.

135
00:06:21,879 --> 00:06:23,560
Your place looks like a model showroom.

136
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:25,560
There's zero life in here.

137
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:40,000
Genius Jiang, is this really necessary?

138
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:42,680
Can you show a guest some basic respect?

139
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:51,160
I'm in a special category right now.

140
00:06:51,839 --> 00:06:54,000
My immunity is low. I must protect myself.

141
00:06:57,519 --> 00:06:59,319
Fine, you really value your life.

142
00:06:59,959 --> 00:07:00,600
Take a look.

143
00:07:00,959 --> 00:07:02,040
See what I bought.

144
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:07,480
I got these at the supermarket downstairs.

145
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:10,000
And this bread, too.

146
00:07:10,319 --> 00:07:11,160
I think this bread

147
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:12,839
suits your current situation perfectly.

148
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,600
I'm not a picky eater.

149
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:46,120
Hard to picture you as someone who cooks.

150
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:55,920
Hair tie.

151
00:07:59,399 --> 00:08:00,199
I'll do it myself.

152
00:08:22,959 --> 00:08:24,600
I just don't want my food

153
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,560
covered in dozens of extra bacteria.

154
00:09:39,399 --> 00:09:41,720
Teeth cleaning is minor, but choose wisely

155
00:09:41,919 --> 00:09:43,799
Always choose a licensed medical facility

156
00:09:43,879 --> 00:09:45,360
for any dental treatment.

157
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,360
The medical staff

158
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:48,799
must undergo rigorous professional training,

159
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:51,360
following One Patient, One Instrument, One Sterilization,

160
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:53,399
with proper sterilization and protocols.

161
00:09:53,639 --> 00:09:55,000
Only this can effectively prevent

162
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:57,639
cross-infection of hepatitis and other diseases,

163
00:09:57,759 --> 00:09:58,679
as well as their transmission.
